data.description: Perfect opportunity to be the homeowner of this beautiful one story home in the highly established Meadow View Community in Bakersfield. This home features 4 Bedrooms, 2 Baths, with a Living Area, Kitchen, Dining Area, Indoor Laundry, and a fully extended den/flex space that can be utilized as a game room, formal living room, formal dining room, or an office. The property features a 2 Car Garage with an open driveway and a low maintenanced back yard. Property was going through a full remodel/renovation but Seller was unable to complete it, however is willing to finish it out depending on the offered price. The home also comes equipped with energy efficient upgrades and solar. It is a lease that has been prepaid by the seller. The Seller also had an appraisal done in its current condition which came back at $365k. Don't Delay! Priced to sell! Your future dream home awaits you!
